Hey guys! Back with another question. Which suit is your favourite? Effects it unlocks doesn't matter but just to look at.
My...
body:
Spider-Man

Hey guys! Back with another question. Which suit is your favourite? Effects it unlocks doesn’t matter but just to look at.

My favourite is the Negative suit because when you’re swinging over the water at night you can look down and there is a perfect reflection of you glowing back.

Follow me here if you’d like sneak peeks of this one, plus any other books I am currently writing that will at some point be posted on AO3 in the coming year.

That is what my main Tumblr account is used for, and I would appreciate it if you would remember this. This Tumblr account + my AO3 account under the same name of this one is for Canon Characters x OCs and that’s it).
